snippet.textDisplay: সরি অর্ণব দা। খুব বাজে শুরু। সেট নিয়ে কথা নাই, কিন্ত গান টা ভালো লাগে নাই। সংগীতের একটা জায়গায় জয়ার থেকে আরো অনেক বেশি গুণী মানুষ কে আনা যেতো। এবং আপনি ফিউশান থেকে একটু বের হয়ে আসেন প্লিজ। গান থেকে অরিজিনাল টাচ টা নাই হয়ে যাচ্ছে। আপনাদের সব গান একই ধাঁচের হয়ে যাচ্ছে।

snippet.textDisplay: 2 min silence for rip of original tati song from the album dub. Totally ruined the vibe of tati song.  And people here talking about Bangladeshi tradition etc. Which I also appreciate.  But u don't want to ruin a song in the name of capitalism. And Arnob may b forgot that coke studio is not about him or his song.  Stop using ur song and make fusion.  There are so many songs and singers who deserve the platform and their solo songs  and performances.  So u should stop revive ur Career here . And open the platform for other singers. Stop making it about you. In every song are putting ur song and making a remix of it , have u lost your creativity ,can't even make a new song. At least respect what u gave us in past. We are glad that we heard how real arnob sounds like. But nowadays what ur r making and doing is totally commercial and some people who actually have knowledge of music and liked ur songs back then., are really disappointed.  Stop making it about urself. Don't ruin the reputation and respect we have for you as an old fan. Give other singers chance a  without including ur old songs . U r good at making fusion and instrumental sounds . So do that. And thank u for this song . People who didn't heard original tati will like it. But not us.
